      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·衛風·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">竹竿.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>籊籊竹竿，以釣于淇，豈不爾思，遠莫致之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>With your long and tapering bamboo rods,
You angle in the K'e.
Do I not think of you?
But I am far away, and cannot get to you.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-weifeng-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
