      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·衛風·005.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">竹竿.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>淇水在右，泉源在左，巧笑之瑳，佩玉之儺。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The waters of the K'e are on the right,
And the Ts'euen-yuen is on the left.
How shine the white teeth through the artful smiles!
How the girdle gems move to the measured steps!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-weifeng-005__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
