      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·衛風·005.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">竹竿.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>淇水滺滺，檜楫松舟，駕言出遊，以寫我憂。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The waters of the K'e flow smoothly:
There are the oars of cedar
And the boats of pine.
Might I but go there in my carriage and ramble,
To dissipate my sorrow!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
